State Regulations

The Attorney General will not accept any registration and/or filing unless all of
the documents and fees required by law and these regulations have been submitted and paid. The organization shall not be in compliance with the law
and these regulations until the registration and/or filing material has been accepted by the Attorney General and may be subject to appropriate
sanctions pursuant to article 7-A and/or the EPTL. Notes
